{"tid":2379014,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"天津一批美國進口啤酒武漢肺炎DNA檢測陽性！中國網民呼籲「買國貨保平安」","createTime":"2021-01-25T02:54:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T07:24:22.000Z","uid":109923,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"f54548b26967914f2d01339b474434372171975b","tid":2379014,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:54:40.000Z","msg":"據天津市防控指揮部披露，天津市寧河區在對轄區某物流公司開展新冠病毒核酸檢測時，發現一批美國進口啤酒整托外包裝樣本的檢測結果呈陽性，不過並未流入市場，已按相關防疫措施進行處置。<br />\n<br />\n經查，這批啤酒的原產地為美國，2020年10月20日至2021年1月6日分批從美國進口運抵天津港，並運至寧河區某物流公司倉庫。<br />\n<br />\n在對工作人員、貨品、外環境等進行核酸檢測時，發現2份啤酒整托外包裝樣本檢測結果呈陽性。<br />\n<br />\n1月24日，經天津市疾控中心復核，結果仍為陽性。<br />\n<br />\n截至1月24日12時，已對庫存涉疫貨品進行封存，未流入天津市場，已開展對貨物、環境的終末消毒。<br />\n<br />\n現場工作人員均採取了防護措施，同時為安全起見，已對存在暴露風險的工作人員及其密切接觸者32人實施管控並採樣，16人核酸檢測結果已出為陰性，其他結果待出，對園區相關企業1066人實施居家隔離並採樣，結果待出。<br />\n<br />\n此前在1月21日，廣西梧州市疾病預防控制中心發佈關於追蹤<strong><span class=\"red\">冷凍雞翅</span></strong>中有關接觸人員的通告。<br />\n<br />\n通告顯示，廣東省中山市一批來自<strong><span class=\"red\">巴西凍雞翅</span></strong>中外包裝核酸檢測結果呈陽性，與該批涉疫冷凍雞翅中同一集裝箱混裝的其他批次產品部分銷往梧州市。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QvgXJdQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQvgXJdQ.png&h=071a380b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d10EWyR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd10EWyR.png&h=c44017f3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EXGHUkw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEXGHUkw.png&h=b15ead6f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uEL5R7c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuEL5R7c.png&h=23cc024f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國內循環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"411b155e506eaa06e90a5b568767fdf6334d85f3","tid":2379014,"uid":12628,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:56:03.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca242ca44715bd9c36ce585563222967194b0111","tid":2379014,"uid":18477,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:58:02.000Z","msg":"雞翼都冇得你食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be98a7e7a4f80243aa9ae9795c18379fbe71a722","tid":2379014,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:58:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持消毒"},{"pid":"de01eb55c50adc4f017c573dd1415687edfceb39","tid":2379014,"uid":155095,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:59:07.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）疫情持續，中國不斷宣稱在進口的食品上驗到新冠病毒，不過世界其它都未檢驗到；中央流行疫情指揮中心今天公布近2個月來的進口食品檢驗結果，230個樣品採樣通通都是陰性。<br />\n<br />\n中國不斷宣稱在各項「進口食品」包裝和食物上驗到新冠病毒，企圖將責任怪罪於食物上，不過至今沒有國家發布任何在食品上驗到病毒的報告。<br />\n<br />\n指揮中心指揮官陳時中指出，世界衛生組織（WHO）及聯合國糧食及農業組織（FAO）等國際組織都說明，目前尚無證據顯示新冠肺炎病毒會透過食品傳播，且無透過食品或其外包裝感染新冠肺炎實例。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/3390072\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F3390072&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABRmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=c22b7c17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F3390072&h=1c20c8c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/3390072</a>"},{"pid":"dd34f411de5ee470a4a88c0a52385696623332e8","tid":2379014,"uid":294518,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:59:10.000Z","msg":"借病毒之名，實現內循環。節省外匯<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 